%% Aciklama: Event-driven bildirim akisi (in-app, push, email, SMS)
%% ---

sequenceDiagram
    participant SVC as Any Service
    participant Queue as Message Queue<br/>(Redis/RabbitMQ)
    participant NS as Notification Service
    participant DB as Preferences DB
    participant InApp as In-App Writer
    participant Push as Push Service<br/>(FCM/APNs)
    participant Email as Email Service<br/>(SendGrid/SES)
    participant SMS as SMS Service<br/>(Twilio)

    SVC->>Queue: Publish event {type: "order.created", user_id, data}

    Queue->>NS: Consume event
    NS->>DB: Kullanici tercihlerini al
    DB-->>NS: {in_app: true, push: true, email: true, sms: false}

    NS->>NS: Template sec + render

    par Paralel gonderim
        NS->>InApp: INSERT notification (zil ikonu icin)
        and
        NS->>Push: Send push {title, body, deep_link}
        Push-->>NS: Delivered
        and
        NS->>Email: Send email {to, subject, html}
        Email-->>NS: Sent
    end

    Note over NS: SMS kapali (kullanici tercihi) -> gonderilmedi
    NS->>DB: Log: notification_sent {channels, status}
